---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">AI Projects & Experiments</p>
      <h1>Production-minded AI work for engineering teams.</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        This space is where I am consolidating selected work around AI-assisted software delivery,
        LLM platform patterns, and internal tools that help engineers move faster with better
        reliability.
      </p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/">Back to main portfolio</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="https://github.com/jdiegosierra" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <h2>Current themes</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>AI-enabled SDLC</h3>
          <p>Developer workflows powered by coding agents, review automation, and pragmatic task acceleration.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>LLM platform reliability</h3>
          <p>Routing, caching, fallbacks, and operational controls for resilient multi-model production setups.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Custom tooling</h3>
          <p>Plugins, commands, skills, and internal agents built around real engineering bottlenecks instead of demos.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel panel-muted">
      <h2>Tooling I am working with</h2>
      <ul class="tags" aria-label="AI tooling and platforms">
        <li>LiteLLM</li>
        <li>Claude Code</li>
        <li>OpenCode</li>
        <li>OpenClaw</li>
        <li>GitHub Actions</li>
        <li>Kubernetes</li>
        <li>Terraform</li>
        <li>Observability</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <h2>What is next</h2>
      <p>
        I am still curating this section. Over time it will include case studies, architecture notes,
        experiments, and concrete examples of how AI is being embedded into delivery workflows and
        platform operations.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    width: min(72rem, calc(100% - 2rem));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .hero,
  .panel {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(9, 16, 27, 0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .panel {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .panel-muted {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(83, 199, 240, 0.1), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04));
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 14ch;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  }

  h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 12rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: transform 160ms ease, box-shadow 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease;
  }

  .button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .button-primary {
    color: #05111d;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(83, 199, 240, 0.22);
  }

  .button-secondary {
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .card {
    padding: 1.1rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .tags li {
    padding: 0.55rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(145, 240, 213, 0.22);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .page {
      width: min(100% - 1rem, 72rem);
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .hero,
    .panel {
      padding: 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 1.2rem;
    }

    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .button {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
